    <a class="article-thumb-wrap" href="/the-interpreter/where-world-jack-ma">
      <div class="article-thumb"
           style="background-image: url('https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/GettyImages-1192058132.jpg?itok=C2Lbtpjz'">
       </div>
    </a>

    <div class="article-title">
      <h3>
        <a href="/the-interpreter/where-world-jack-ma">
          Where in the world is Jack Ma?
        </a>
      </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="pv-sm">
      <div class="article-precede">
        Explaining the “disappearance” of China’s most charismatic businessman takes an appreciation of Xi Jinping Thought.
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</div>
													

